reviewText:
I own all Elemental games, and while this is by far the best of them, it never grew on me. I love 4X games, and probably own most of the known ones, but this one feels like it's lacking something.

**A few points:**

* tons of content in this game: items, loot, weapons, spells, there's a lot of them;
* mob variety: a lot of variety, and they scale well among all levels and all of them have a little flavor description;
* total lack of empire management: nothing at all; no empire plan" or "social policies" or "virtues" or anything similar to adapt your empire;
* diplomacy is rather dull and almost useless
